name: Smitten DVD & Black Paintings EP Combo Pack
description:
CLEARANCE SALE!

Australia's Rock Climbing & BASE jumping film & The Black Paintings EP featuring the tracks 'Milk & Honey and A Fine Line'!

Starring Lucky Chance, Chris Webb Parsons, Lee Cossey, Ben Cossey, Zac Vertrees, Jarmila Tyrril, James Kassay, Tom Farrell & Monique Forestier. 

Running Time 93 minutes, with over 50 minutes of extras!

Australian version. For mature audiences ages 15 and up. Adult themes and Coarse language. PAL.

Black Paintings - Milk And Honey EP

Featuring the singles "Milk & Honey" and "A Fine Line" as featured in Smitten The Movie. 

These recordings are a collection of Australian stories with particular themes of religion and women.

The Black Paintings are a rhythm and blues band from South Sydney Australia. 

Track Listing:

Milk & Honey
Corporate Love
And If It Rains?
Lets Burn Together Baby
A Fine Line
The Marble Arch

Listen to Milk & Honey: 

http://vimeo.com/16456058
